content: Dear devs, This game just need some slight improvements, then it would be pretty fun to play. There are a few things that you guys need to improve, -make the game supports major languages such as English, Chinese, etc. -make the HUD customizable -improve the efficiency of the AI ( but you guys don't really have to focus on this first, just those 2 above ) This game has a LOT of potential, really, a lot. So don't waste your hard work. Keep up! I'll be waiting.
I want refund, this game has no language option.

Good game. Very well thought out gameplay. Just needs an English translation and In survival needs to be easier to get ammo. Also would like multiplayer! Good work devs. Please update to english thanks
it s so potential, please add more mode, multiplayer, language option
Really good game...only in Russian. Patch to English and 5 stars.
